        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= current_admin.email %></li>
          <li><strong>Role:</strong> Super Admin</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Project Information Section -->
      <div class="mt-4">
        <h3>About the Project</h3>
        <p>This is a comprehensive <strong>Crime Reporting System</strong> that facilitates the reporting and management of crime cases. Key features include:</p>
