          <li>Branch management for police stations</li>
          <li>Case assignment and status updates by police</li>
          <li>User-friendly interfaces for admins, police, and users</li>
          <li>Detailed reporting and analytics for crime data</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This system ensures seamless communication between users and law enforcement agencies, enhancing efficiency and transparency in crime reporting and case management.</p>
      </div>
    </div>


